com.googlecode.n_orm.utils

Class AggregatingIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.n_orm.utils.AggregatingIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CloseableIterator<Row>, CloseableKeyIterator, Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterator<Row>

    public class AggregatingIterator
extends Object
implements CloseableKeyIterator
    An CloseableIterator composite able to iterate over a set of CloseableIterators. Elements are selected from composed iterators so that they are iterated in an ordered way. In case an element with same id is found from different iterators, an exception is thrown, unless merge(Row, CloseableKeyIterator, Row, CloseableKeyIterator) is overridden.
